{"tid":1557601,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Fact checked！申請做陪審員文宣有錯漏！","createTime":"2019-09-10T07:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T06:42:56.000Z","uid":283449,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"095417d24f9a975e9b8777e3fe9596abda983887","tid":1557601,"uid":283449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:37:07.000Z","msg":"1. <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jdcoggv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjdcoggv.jpg&h=38f8e6d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n申請做陪審員要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">寫信話自己申請做陪審員</span></span>，因為 ROP18 係多用途的，就咁一張 form 入境處就只會幫你 update 個人資料。<br />\n但如果有埋學歷證明既話，問左都可能幫你做。<br />\n<br />\n2. <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TaeBBhR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTaeBBhR.png&h=91c34037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同有冇大學學歷無關</span></span>！本地大學畢業都唔代表你一定被納入陪審員名單，因為大學成日做漏野，同埋有冇本地大學學位並唔係成為陪審員既考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇被納入名單係睇有冇收過書面通知。</span></span>如果你本地大學畢業，但冇收過書名通知，咁你好大可能唔係陪審員名單入面，除左咁啱張書名通知寄失左。<br />\n<br />\n另外，電話係查詢唔到自己有否被納入陪審員名單，因為私隱問題，一定要寫信。寫得信查詢自己係咪，不如你跟步驟申請過啦。<br />\n<br />\n最後，唔該整理一下自己既 social media，做人唔好太偏激，要中立，知道嘛？<br />\n控方有無限次有因由反對某 d 人出任陪審員。<br />\n<br />\n以下係小弟自己執既文宣，請廣傳。<br />\n自己義士自己救。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N8Obp9m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN8Obp9m.jpg&h=f79c69e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c81289784b1ec41317dc971dfdb57b1ed41e0dc","tid":1557601,"uid":1690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:49:41.000Z","msg":"控方有權查核個人社交媒體咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a33344c4edcf3aaa1b849102f1f383eebb84698","tid":1557601,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:07:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=5cfbb303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"9b4bca4b8b0c0deb9afed54f9e11b82be93931ee","tid":1557601,"uid":36445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c81289784b1ec41317dc971dfdb57b1ed41e0dc","tid":1557601,"uid":1690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:49:41.000Z","msg":"控方有權查核個人社交媒體咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:08:48.000Z","msg":"係囉 除非全部地球po架姐"},{"pid":"655ad2458ec5af31cfcebec9a16efb7cb8f5844a","tid":1557601,"uid":235635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:08:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"809d9b098964e6c3fd9c587616629e5fafc9bd29","tid":1557601,"uid":283449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c81289784b1ec41317dc971dfdb57b1ed41e0dc","tid":1557601,"uid":1690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T07:49:41.000Z","msg":"控方有權查核個人社交媒體咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:22:24.000Z","msg":"有權問問題，如問你 fb account。<br />\n然後佢助手即刻 check咪得。"},{"pid":"05fb3dd2afc1fc2db3004550527536da66b8576b","tid":1557601,